1950;;The Dragon of Pendragon Castle;;British;;John Baxter;;Robin Netscher, Hilary Rennie, Graham Moffatt;;family;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Dragon_of_Pendragon_Castle;;Mr. Ferber (Leslie Bradley) is an old man living in Pendragon Castle along with his two grandchildren Bobby(David Hannaford) and Paddy (Graham Moffatt) who find a small dragon to heat their castle. The dragon helps them to find hidden treasure in the castle.